<p class="mars">If [email address] is registered to an account, you’ll receive an email with instructions to reset your password.</p>
<div class="guidance js-details" data-guidance-label="Help with email" data-guidance="Help with email" data-hide-label="Help with email" data-show-label="Help with email">
