  <div class="guidance__content mars">
    <div>
      <p>If you don’t receive this within 15 minutes, try the following:
        </p><ul>
            <li class="list__item">Check your spam folder</li>
            <li class="list__item">Check that you've entered your email address correctly</li>
            <li class="list__item">Ensure that you've registered an account using this email address</li>
        </ul>
      <p></p>
      <p>If you’re still having problems, call us on <a class="u-ws-n" href="tel:+44-300-1234-931">0300 1234 931</a> or send an email to <a href="mailto:surveys@ons.gov.uk?Subject=Not%20received%20create%20account%20email">surveys@ons.gov.uk</a>.</p>
